data.description:
*Seller has since removed brick wallpaper and painted master bath since listing*
This is the one you've been searching for!! This well taken care of home sits, overlooking a catfish stocked pond, on almost 8.5 beautiful acres. Plenty of room to roam and play in the front yard! The home has a formal sitting area, formal dining room, ample amount of storage space and large bedrooms and closets, including a flex space that can be used as a large office or small guest room. The gorgeous stone fireplace with built in wooden bookshelves and lower cabinets really is a statement piece. Come explore this private, country living home today! *Bring ALL Offers!*
